{"tid":1233623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢位同路人已經道出曬宜家場抗爭面臨咩問題喇，醒就醒，唔醒就救唔返","createTime":"2019-06-16T19:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T20:15:00.000Z","uid":161430,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"136932b4908067f47a317488b2cb58969ebbbca3","tid":1233623,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPsOUBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPsOUBQ.jpg&h=4222ecd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 呢個人比人當係鬼<br />\n2. 有人話「香港人贏緊」，呢位兄弟反對，但比人屌返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n果啲邊個邊個係鬼、唔好比人有口實既論調出曬黎，<br />\n仲有覺得自己贏緊既感覺都出曬黎，<br />\n行緊舊路喇又開始，<br />\n大家要小心，醒既好醒，唔醒就真係救唔返場抗爭"},{"pid":"132e84929c119613fae338aed34053e7d02456b7","tid":1233623,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:58:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"165ddbc1208205be9f72368dbdfd3db5bd7802f0","tid":1233623,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:58:45.000Z","msg":"你貼上黎乜撚都唔打格想做乜"},{"pid":"afa6ea47c6276bce8af70d20f1a5adf0f99571e8","tid":1233623,"uid":45206,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:59:36.000Z","msg":"巴打 唔好再分鬼 <br />\n我見到你好多comment都好勇武 我好贊同<br />\n但係我而家認為真正重要嘅只有真普選<br />\n其他嘅議題都係off track<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n必須重提真普選！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233485</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f63927579dc60dc8d9c94ee700c4dd4f62a7685c","tid":1233623,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:00:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e29aac73809cf78f68b49ce48cc04fabbd2fa3b5","tid":1233623,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2cfa09e5b75c2e473b3035a5c5640c36d2adfb","tid":1233623,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited